oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Pre-Weaning and Post-Weaning Nutrition
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Williams, Danny L.
Mahoney, John. H.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: animal health
preconditioning
cow/calf
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Animal health is an important aspect of a preconditioning program; however, average daily gain and feed efficiency are extremely important if the program is to be profitable for the cow:calf producer. Not all calves are stressed to the same degree and as a result, not all calves will respond equally to a given treatment or nutritional level.
